# 詞: **睇怕**

1. 佢睇到老鼠就睇怕，一點都唔使勇。 (He's afraid of mice and isn't brave at all.)
2. 我睇到高處就睇怕，唔敢坐吊車。 (I'm afraid of heights and don't dare ride a cable car.)
3. 佢睇到黑暗就睇怕，每晚都要開燈睏覺。 (He's afraid of the dark and always sleeps with the light on.)
4. 我睇到蛇就睇怕，一見到就大叫。 (I'm afraid of snakes and scream when I see one.)
5. 佢睇到鬼故事就睇怕，唔敢一個人睇電影。 (He's afraid of ghost stories and doesn't dare watch movies alone.)
6. 我睇到蜘蛛就睇怕，一見到就跑。 (I'm afraid of spiders and run away when I see one.)
7. 佢睇到血就睇怕，唔使做手術。 (He's afraid of blood and can't handle surgery.)
8. 我睇到飛機就睇怕，每次坐飛機都會緊張。 (I'm afraid of flying and get nervous every time I take a plane.)
9. 佢睇到狗就睇怕，唔敢一個人行街。 (He's afraid of dogs and doesn't dare walk alone on the street.)
10. 我睇到考試就睇怕，每次都會手抖。 (I'm afraid of exams and my hands shake every time.)

